  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eNestled within the streets of Le Marais, a jewel of Parisian heritage has been reborn. The newly renovated top-floor \u003ca href=\"https://www.lichellesilvestry.com/marais-renovation-decoration-project\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003epied-à-terre\u003c/a\u003e is perched within a 17th-century building, weaving a tapestry of time-honored elegance with contemporary sophistication. The past and present are blurred as one travels throughout the property – exposed beams and a stone fireplace date back to 1660, followed by an 18th-century entrance adorned with intricate ironwork. Designer \u003cstrong\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.lichellesilvestry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eLichelle Silvestry\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e used the building’s historical character as a canvas for modern prose, emphasizing natural materials such as wood, linen, and marble.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-parisian-pied-a-terres-merges-classic-and-contemporary/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-12/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-557681\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-12-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A corner of the living room, featuring a sculptural armchair, a jute rug, and a floor lamp\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-12-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-12-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-12-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-12-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA large jute rug and a custom linen sofa anchor the living space, complemented by a walnut coffee table from The Invisible Collection. Furniture selections like the by Lassen armchair and the Cassina Utrecht chair frame the room’s centerpiece, a restored 18th-century mirror sourced from a local antique market. Silvestry also custom-built a low storage unit to maximize functionality, paired with artwork by Spanish artist Javier Torres, creating a harmonious blend of art and design.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-parisian-pied-a-terres-merges-classic-and-contemporary/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-15/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-557683\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-15-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A detailed view of the living room, featuring a custom sideboard and abstract art\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-15-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-15-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-15-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-15-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-parisian-pied-a-terres-merges-classic-and-contemporary/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-14/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-557682\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\