g room with exposed wooden beams, linen curtains, and a cozy seating area\" width=\"810\" height=\"1013\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-1-810x1013.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-1-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-1-768x960.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-1-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-1.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-parisian-pied-a-terres-merges-classic-and-contemporary/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-557674\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-2-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A Parisian living room featuring a grand, gilded mirror above a fireplace\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-2-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-2-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-2-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-2-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-parisian-pied-a-terres-merges-classic-and-contemporary/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-557675\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=