\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003eFarrow and Ball\u003c/a\u003e-painted cabinetry and a distinguished \u003ca href=\"https://www.lacanche.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eLacanche\u003c/a\u003e stove mingle with Calacatta marble and unlacquered brass, their dialogue mediated by an imposing oak dining table completed alongside a set of \u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/tag/carl-hansen/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003eCarl Hansen \u0026amp; Søn\u003c/a\u003e Wishbone chairs. The primary bedroom offers a serene retreat, with muted tones that enhance the view of the private courtyard. A silk-mix rug and a vintage Venini chandelier add subtle luxury, while modern furniture selections, including a sheepskin settee and a Fontana Arte floor lamp, maintain clean lines.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-parisian-pied-a-terres-merges-classic-and-contemporary/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-4/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-557676\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-4-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A close-up of a sophisticated kitchen featuring marble countertops\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-4-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-4-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-4-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-4-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-parisian-pied-a-terres-merges-classic-and-contemporary/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-8/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-557679\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-8-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A cozy nook with a plush linen sofa, framed by white-washed walls and contemporary artwork\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-8-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-8-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-8-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-8-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-8.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/a-parisian-pied-a-terres-merges-classic-and-contemporary/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-5/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-557677\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-5-810x1080.jpg\" alt=\"A serene bedroom with muted tones, a plush bed, and a vintage Venini chandelier\" width=\"810\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-5-810x1080.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-5-800x1067.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-5-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-terre-lichelle-silvestry-5-1152x1536.jpg 1152w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/09/parisian-pied-a-t